The paper discusses the analysis and integration of social network services, which falls under the sub-category of Social and Information Networks (cs.SI). The paper also discusses the challenges of efficient information retrieval and accurately resolving duplicate entities, which are common problems in Information Retrieval (cs.IR), Databases (cs.DB), and Data Mining (cs.SD). The proposed method also involves link mining, which is a technique used in Natural Language Processing (cs.CL).
